Class User

java.lang.Object
items.Item
items.users.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Stringifiable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Applicant, Manager
public class User extends Item implements Stringifiable
The User class represents a user in the system. It is an abstract class that defines the basic properties and behaviors of a user such as ID, password, age, and marital status.
